        Home Loan Pre-Approval When Selling in Brisbane: What It Means for Your Buyers
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        If a buyer says they are pre-approved, what does that actually mean? Here is what Brisbane sellers need to know about pre-approval, formal approval, and managing conditional offers with confidence.
      </p>
